high_descs: Move a bit to the right in front of the table
Pick up the knife on the table
Turn left, go forward turn right at the counter
Slice the tomato on the counter
Turn around, go forward, turn left and go to the fridge
Put the knife in the fridge
Turn around, go forward, turn right and go to the counter
Pick up a tomato slice
Go in front of the stove
Put the tomato slice in the microwave, start the microwave, wait, pick up the tomato slice

Put the tomato slice in the fridge

Place the knife in the fridge.
Turn left and walk across the room to face the tomato.
Pick up the slice of tomato on the counter.

Heat the tomato slice in the microwave and remove it.
Turn right and step forward to face the fridge.
Place the tomato slice in the fridge.
